Loops
-Repetitive Tasks
-Group of something and you wish to perform some action over that group...

-while loop
  define a variable
  while(condition)
  {
      this code will execute only if condition is true
      I/D;
  }
-for loop
  for(define a variable;condition;I/D)
  {
      this code will execute only if condition is true

  }

-advanced for loop